Minor.

Graph comparison does not raise exceptions anymore. (patch by jonathansternberg).
Fixing a bug regarding linking, unlinking and relinking a hypernode to a hyperedge (patch by emanuelez)
Bellman-Ford algorithm now works for unconnected graphs.
